---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ProjectCard from '../components/ProjectCard.astro';
import { projects } from '../data/projects';
import herobg from '../assets/images/hero-bg.jpeg?url'
---

<Layout title="Junior Web Developer Portfolio">
  <main>
    <section class="hero reveal" id="home">
        <img class="hero-img" src={herobg} alt="">
        <div class="hero-copy reveal">
          <p class="eyebrow">Junior Web Developer</p>
          <h1>Hi, I'm Michael</h1>
          <h3> 
            I'm a self taught frontend developer that likes to 
            build apps around the things I actually care about, films, music, books, 
            because I think the best way to learn is to build something you'd actually use.
          </h3>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="button" href="#projects">View projects</a>
            <a class="button button-secondary" href="#contact">Contact</a>
          </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section about-section reveal" id="about">
      <div class="split-section">
        <div class="split-card title">
          <p class="eyebrow">About Me</p>
          <h2>Who I am<br>as a developer</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="split-card bento-side">
          <div class="bento-grid">
            <div class="bento-tile tile-origin">
              <span class="tile-label">Origin</span>
              <p>Before I got into web development I was headed toward data analytics. After enjoying SQL more than anything else, I realized I like to code. I needed something that still let me build and problem solve, so I started learning through Google Coursera as a safe pick.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-tile tile-badge">
              <p class="tile-stat">Self-Taught</p>
              <p class="tile-sub">Frontend Developer</p>
              <ul>
                <li>Likes working with my hands</li>
                <li>Love the creative freedom from it</li>
                <li>Enjoys murder mysteries so loves the problem solving</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-tile tile-drive">
              <span class="tile-label">What clicked</span>
              <p>I realized pretty quickly I enjoyed the SQL and coding parts more than anything else in the syllabus. The building aspect pulled me in harder than the rest. So I chose this path. One that lets me keep growing and make things that genuinely inspire me.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bento-tile tile-stack">
              <span class="tile-label">Working with</span>
              <div class="tile-tags">
                <span>TypeScript</span>
                <span>React</span>
                <span>Next.js</span>
                <span>Astro</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

      <section class="section projects-section reveal" id="projects">
      <div class="section-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>
        <h2>Featured work</h2>
        <p>
          These projects show how my work has grown from vanilla TypeScript to React and
          Next.js, with real app logic and polish.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="projects-grid">
        {projects.map((project) => (
          <ProjectCard project={project} />
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section approach-section reveal">
      <div class="split-section split-reverse">
        <div class="split-card title">
          <p class="eyebrow">My Approach</p>
          <h2>How I build</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="split-card approach-copy">
          <div class="approach-points">
            <div class="approach-point">
              <span class="point-num">01</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Start with something real</strong>
                <p>Every project I've built started as something I actually wanted to use. That keeps the work honest and the decisions clear.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-point">
              <span class="point-num">02</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Get it working, then get it right</strong>
                <p>I build iteratively. Shipping a rough version first teaches you more than planning it perfectly on paper.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="approach-point">
              <span class="point-num">03</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Write code for the next person</strong>
                <p>I name things clearly and keep logic easy to follow. Code is read far more than it's written.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  

  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
.hero {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto;
  height: 100vh;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(8, 12, 28, 0.52);
  z-index: 0;
}
.hero-bg {
  position: relative;
}

.hero-img{
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  display: block;
  object-fit: cover;
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
}
.hero-copy {
  max-width: 680px;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
}
.eyebrow {
  margin: 0 0 1rem;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #2563eb;
}
.hero .eyebrow {
  color:#2563eb;
}
.hero h1 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4vw, 4.7rem);
  line-height: 1.02;
}
.hero h3 {
  color: #f4f2fb;
}
.hero h1, h3 {
  color: white;
}
.hero-copy p {
  max-width: 620px;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: #334155;
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
}
.hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin-top: 2rem;
}
.split-section {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 3rem;
  text-wrap: wrap;
}
.split-card {
  width: 100%;
}
.section .title .eyebrow {
  /* text-align: center;
  font-size: 1rem; */
}
.section .title h2 {
  font-size: 3.4rem;
}
.about-section {
  background: #080d1a;
}
.about-section .eyebrow {
  color: #2563eb;
}
.about-section .split-card.title h2 {
  color: white;
}
.bento-side {
  height: auto;
}
.bento-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.bento-tile {
  padding: 1.75rem;
  border-radius: 1rem;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
  border: 1px solid rgba(99, 179, 237, 0.1);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.bento-tile p {
  color: #94a3b8;
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  margin: 0.6rem 0 0;
}
.tile-label {
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #2563eb;
}
.tile-badge {
  background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
  border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
  justify-content: center;
}
.tile-stat {
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: white;
  margin: 0;
  line-height: 1.2;
}
.tile-sub {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: #93c5fd;
  margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
}
.tile-badge ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
  margin: 1rem 0 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.5rem;
}
.tile-badge li {
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: #93c5fd;
  padding-left: 1rem;
  position: relative;
}
.tile-badge li::before {
  content: '·';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: #2563eb;
  font-weight: 700;
}
.tile-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-top: 0.85rem;
}
.tile-tags span {
  padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);
  color: #93c5fd;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.approach-section {
  background: #0d1117;
}
.approach-section .eyebrow {
  color: #d97706;
}
.approach-section .split-card.title h2 {
  color: white;
}
.split-reverse {
  flex-direction: row-reverse;
}
.approach-copy {
  height: auto;
}
.approach-points {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2rem;
}
.approach-point {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.25rem;
  align-items: flex-start;
}
.point-num {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: #d97706;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  padding-top: 0.25rem;
  min-width: 2rem;
}
.approach-point strong {
  display: block;
  color: white;
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.approach-point p {
  color: #94a3b8;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin: 0;
}
.button {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
  background: #2563eb;
  border-radius: 999px;
  color: white;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 700;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.button-secondary {
  background: #f8fafc;
  color: #0f172a;
  border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.3);
}
.hero-panel {
  display: grid;
  gap: 1rem;
}
.panel-card {
  padding: 2rem;
  border-radius: 1.5rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
}
.panel-card h2 {
  margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
}
.panel-card ul {
  margin: 0;
  padding-left: 1.25rem;
  color: #475569;
}
.panel-card li {
  margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
}
.section {
  padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
}
.section-copy {
  max-width: 680px;
}
.section h2 {
  margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 2.5vw, 2.75rem);
}
.skill-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 0.85rem;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(12rem, 1fr));
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
}
.skill-grid span {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 0.95rem 1rem;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1);
  color: #0f172a;
  font-weight: 600;
}
.small-note {
  max-width: 720px;
  margin-top: 1.25rem;
  color: #475569;
}
.projects-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(18rem, 1fr));
  margin-top: 2rem;
}
@media (min-width: 900px) {
  .hero {
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.1fr) minmax(320px, 0.9fr);
    align-items: center;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .about-section .split-section {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }
  .about-section .split-card.title h2 {
    font-size: 2.6rem;
  }
}
@media (max-width: 720px) {
  .about-section .split-card.title h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
  }
  .about-section .bento-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .about-section .bento-tile {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
}
</style>
